properties.name: Malaga, Spain
properties.description: Posted by CstmswapsTwo friends of mine own a flat in a lovely place in Calahonda. Old type, Spanish dwelling, with original fittings and superb balcony view of the aquamarine sea. Nightlife was ten minutes away. Loads of expats. And just one or two "Dodgy Daves", with broad noses! Fab night at "Bunny\'s", a drag cabaret club. Of course most of the audience was British, so we all had a good old knees up. I also love foraging around in the local supermarkets. Everything seems so much better than our stuff. It\'s just psychological, really. Although I couldn\'t get enough of Spanish tomatoes.
